General.Name: Newfield Resources Ltd
General.Description: Newfield Resources Limited engages in the mine development, stope mining, and mineral exploration activities primarily in Australia and Africa. It explores for diamonds and gold deposits. The company's flagship project is the Tongo diamond project, which covers an area over 134 square kilometers in eastern Sierra Leone. Newfield Resources Limited was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Applecross, Australia.
